a protest with India against the intrusion and violation of the
Bangladesh air space by an Indian Air Force helicopter recently,
local press reported today.
</P>
<P>
Early this month, the opposition leader Khaleda Zia, who has
been accusing the government of selling out sovereignty to India,
expressed concern over the landing of the Indian helicopter.
</P>
<P>
