Some export-import food companies in the Mekong Delta have also
won contracts for shipping overseas high-quality rice. The price
was 242 to 245 U.S. dollars per ton, up by 15 U.S. dollars.
</P>
<P>
The winter-spring crop in Vietnam yielded an estimated 13
million tons, nearly one million tons more than last year's crop.
