France from qualifying for the 1994 finals, made it 2-0 just after
half-time, playmaker Krasimir Balakov scored the third from the
penalty spot and Yordan Letchkov, another player returning after a
falling out with Bonev, wrapped up the three points in the 82nd
minute. 
