BUDAPEST, June 8 (Xinhua) -- Hungary, who went behind to Norway
after just nine minutes, came back to force a 1-1 draw in A World
Cup European Zone Group Three qualifier here on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Rudi put Norway ahead but Kovacs made it 1-1 after 20 minutes.
</P>
<P>
